# Drop your library's branding assets here. Filenames are auto-detected:
#
#   Logo:   logo.svg | logo.png | logo.jpg | logo.webp
#   Video:  welcome.mp4 | welcome.webm | welcome.mov
#
# To override the filename or use a remote URL instead, set KIOSK_LOGO_URL /
# KIOSK_WELCOME_VIDEO_URL in .env. See README → "Branding".
#
# NOTE: This folder is committed so the path exists, but the binary assets you
# drop here should NOT be committed if they are large or org-specific — add
# patterns to .gitignore as needed (e.g. /apps/kiosk/public/branding/*.*).
